cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CV 

The paper deals with machine learning, specifically linear regression models, and the manipulation of training data to influence the results of predictive models. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and security and privacy (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses optimization frameworks (cs.AI), statistical attacks (cs.DS), and datasets related to real estate and healthcare (cs.CV).
